## last variable

Returns the last element of the given list or string.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
last: <T extends string | unknown[]>(val: T) => Last<T>
```

## Example 1


```ts
// String
last('hello') // 'o'

```

## Example 2


```ts
// Array
last('hello', 'new', 'world') // 'world'
last([]) // undefined
last(['one', 2, 3, 4]) // 4

```
